  <p class="page-hero-eyebrow">✦ The story behind the blog</p>
  <h1>Hi, I'm The Unchained Girl</h1>
  <p>A traveler, food lover, and storyteller from Bangladesh — exploring the world on my own terms, one honest story at a time.</p>
</div>

<div class="about-body">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <h2>Who am I?</h2>
      <p>I'm a Bangladeshi woman who decided that the world was too big and life too short to stay in one place. <strong>The Unchained Girl</strong> is my space to share the real, unfiltered experience of travel — the beautiful moments, the budget struggles, the unexpected meals, and the connections that change you.</p>
      <p>I write about travel from Bangladesh and abroad — trekking through hills, eating my way through street markets, finding peace in nature, and connecting with communities that remind me why travel matters.</p>
      <p>This blog is for every curious soul who wants to explore the world honestly — without the Instagram filter, without the luxury budget, and without the pretense. Just real stories from the road.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-img">🌍</div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-facts">
    <div class="fact-card">
      <div class="fact-num">🇧🇩</div>
